760
01:11:16,560 --> 01:11:19,500
Okay, then.

761
01:11:19,500 --> 01:11:24,320
I, Go Yoo Han, Yeon Woo's closest friend, will head home now.

762
01:11:24,320 --> 01:11:26,320
Alright, you should quickly go home.

763
01:11:26,320 --> 01:11:28,880
Your parents will be worried.

764
01:11:29,770 --> 01:11:31,170
- Choi Yeon Woo.
- Yeah?

765
01:11:31,170 --> 01:11:32,580
Aren't you going to walk me home?

766
01:11:32,580 --> 01:11:37,480
Guess you're not that close after all. I guess only you consider that.

767
01:11:39,280 --> 01:11:41,860
Aunt, I'll be back.

768
01:11:41,860 --> 01:11:44,850
Hurry back soon. I'm hungry.

769
01:11:44,850 --> 01:11:49,330
Oh right! Ramen...

770
01:11:49,330 --> 01:11:51,130
I'll be back.

771
01:11:52,350 --> 01:11:54,380
What is he talking about?

772
01:11:57,290 --> 01:12:00,410
Why are you so elated?

773
01:12:00,410 --> 01:12:02,460
Is it because you're happy your aunt is home?

774
01:12:02,460 --> 01:12:04,130
Put your mask on.

775
01:12:04,130 --> 01:12:05,000
My mask!

776
01:12:05,000 --> 01:12:07,170
You haven't been wearing it since earlier.

777
01:12:07,170 --> 01:12:09,800
- Hey, are you okay?
- Yeah.

778
01:12:09,800 --> 01:12:11,550
You scared me.

779
01:12:11,550 --> 01:12:13,380
Hey! My hair.

780
01:12:17,650 --> 01:12:22,650
I can still see colors. Decoloring hasn't happened yet.

781
01:12:22,650 --> 01:12:25,860
Really? It must mean you've gotten used to it.

782
01:12:25,860 --> 01:12:29,450
You've gotten more used to it because you have feelings for me!

783
01:12:29,450 --> 01:12:32,610
No, that's not it.

784
01:12:35,920 --> 01:12:39,800
That over there is blue.

785
01:12:41,350 --> 01:12:43,390
That over there is yellow.

786
01:12:43,390 --> 01:12:45,790
Yes, yellow.

787
01:12:48,890 --> 01:12:51,720
That over there is...

788
01:12:53,010 --> 01:12:54,850
- Neon
- Neon?

789
01:12:54,850 --> 01:12:57,190
Because the original color was mixed with luminescence.

790
01:12:57,190 --> 01:13:01,960
That is blue mixed with luminescence, so it's neon blue.

791
01:13:01,960 --> 01:13:07,530
Yeon Woo, what color do you think that café's sign over there is?

792
01:13:07,530 --> 01:13:09,520
Yellow?

