820
01:15:32,480 --> 01:15:34,790
I have to run away.

821
01:15:45,000 --> 01:15:49,410
The feeling of despair is taking over. I'm losing energy.

822
01:15:49,410 --> 01:15:54,050
When Yoo Han leaves, I'm abandoned in

823
01:15:54,050 --> 01:15:56,380
an empty world.

824
01:16:18,340 --> 01:16:20,720
Did you meet a Probe?

825
01:16:21,560 --> 01:16:26,010
Go Yoo Han is your Probe, right?

826
01:16:28,320 --> 01:16:30,020
Yes.

827
01:16:30,980 --> 01:16:32,480
- Let's transfer schools.
- I don't want to.

828
01:16:32,480 --> 01:16:34,630
- And let's move.
- I said I don't want to.

829
01:16:34,630 --> 01:16:36,830
Then, what will you do?

830
01:16:37,760 --> 01:16:40,670
I'll try to endure it, Aunt.

831
01:16:40,670 --> 01:16:43,390
I'm different. I'm different from the other Monos.

832
01:16:43,390 --> 01:16:46,520
This is mine. It's mine.

833
01:16:46,520 --> 01:16:49,520
Do you not know how much despair you will suffer?

834
01:16:49,520 --> 01:16:51,890
How will you endure that?

835
01:16:51,890 --> 01:16:54,960
I lost my sister. I can't lose you.

836
01:16:54,960 --> 01:16:57,540
No, I don't want to. I mean it.

837
01:16:57,540 --> 01:16:59,820
Don't say that.

838
01:17:08,010 --> 01:17:09,990
I'm sorry, Yeon Woo.

839
01:17:09,990 --> 01:17:12,430
It's all my fault.

840
01:17:19,560 --> 01:17:23,340
Yoo Han isn't coming again. He's getting tested.

841
01:17:23,340 --> 01:17:26,800
When they get into a debut group, they get their phones taken away, placed in dorms...

842
01:17:26,800 --> 01:17:29,350
Does that mean we won't be seeing Yoo Han anymore?

843
01:17:29,350 --> 01:17:30,750
I guess so.

844
01:17:30,750 --> 01:17:33,130
He really might not come in anymore.

845
01:17:35,030 --> 01:17:40,390
If I kidnap Go Yoo Han,

846
01:17:40,390 --> 01:17:42,650
how do you think he'd feel?

847
01:17:44,950 --> 01:17:47,390
What kind of nonsense is that?

848
01:17:50,460 --> 01:17:54,720
Will you become a monster because you've been bitten by one?

849
01:17:55,570 --> 01:17:58,950
A monster came and took my mother away.

850
01:17:58,950 --> 01:18:04,430
Am I not allowed to be a monster and keep Yoo Han by my side?

851
01:18:10,420 --> 01:18:14,570
You guys sound so serious. What kind of joke is that?

852
01:18:14,570 --> 01:18:18,210
You know Go Yoo Han. If you kidnap him, he'll be the one to make sure the doors are locked

853
01:18:18,210 --> 01:18:20,600
in case you'll let him go.

854
01:18:29,270 --> 01:18:31,420
What's with the atmosphere?

855
01:18:32,470 --> 01:18:35,450
Kang Min Jae is the one who sees the truth.

856
01:18:35,450 --> 01:18:39,550
I'm getting ready to be a monster.

857
01:20:17,600 --> 01:20:21,160
Choi Yeon Woo, don't do anything foolish.

858
01:20:21,160 --> 01:20:24,440
I bought a cellphone because it was broken.

859
01:20:26,770 --> 01:20:29,490
Seeing you makes me think of something.

860
01:20:29,490 --> 01:20:30,500
What?

861
01:20:30,500 --> 01:20:32,140
My sister.

862
01:20:32,140 --> 01:20:37,000
You're just like my sister before she brought her husband home.

863
01:20:37,000 --> 01:20:39,150
What are you talking about?

864
01:20:39,150 --> 01:20:43,590
It felt like she was up to something,

865
01:20:43,590 --> 01:20:45,580
but I couldn't quite figure it out.

866
01:20:45,580 --> 01:20:47,940
I'm not doing anything.

867
01:21:15,920 --> 01:21:20,250
[How to tie a noose knot]

868
01:21:25,960 --> 01:21:27,970
Yeon Woo!

869
01:21:43,210 --> 01:21:46,010
Are you okay?

870
01:21:46,010 --> 01:21:47,570
You came to school today.

871
01:21:47,570 --> 01:21:51,760
Yeah. I came early because I missed you.

872
01:21:55,990 --> 01:21:59,060
What happened? Did you get hurt?

873
01:22:03,000 --> 01:22:06,270
How will these wounds look to Go Yoo Han?

874
01:22:06,270 --> 01:22:10,160
What happened? Are you sure you're okay?

875
01:22:10,160 --> 01:22:13,340
- By any chance, does your Aunt abuse—
- No, it's nothing like that.

876
01:22:13,340 --> 01:22:15,760
Then why in the world is your arm like that?

877
01:22:15,760 --> 01:22:18,680
The person you should be worrying about is yourself, not me.

878
01:22:18,680 --> 01:22:21,880
I told you before. I'm a Mono.

879
01:22:21,880 --> 01:22:23,350
And you're a Probe.

880
01:22:23,350 --> 01:22:26,910
Monos will inevitably do unspeakable acts against Probes.

881
01:22:26,910 --> 01:22:33,270
Because Monos don't want to lose sight of the world that the Probes have shown.

882
01:22:41,090 --> 01:22:43,650
I got hurt from organizing some stuff yesterday.

883
01:22:43,650 --> 01:22:45,300
If that's the case, that's a relief.

884
01:22:45,300 --> 01:22:49,080
Let's go. I'll put some ointment on it in the nurse's office.

885
01:22:54,760 --> 01:22:58,120
Your pupils...

886
01:22:58,120 --> 01:23:00,630
Is caramel a shade of brown?

887
01:23:00,630 --> 01:23:01,770
Yes.

888
01:23:01,770 --> 01:23:06,520
Tell me other shades of brown other than caramel.

889
01:23:07,340 --> 01:23:09,380
Sounds good.

890
01:23:09,380 --> 01:23:13,310
Cocoa, red bean, jujube,

891
01:23:13,310 --> 01:23:17,050
copper, brick,

892
01:23:17,050 --> 01:23:19,300
maroon, chocolate,

893
01:23:19,300 --> 01:23:21,650
chestnut, coffee,

894
01:23:21,650 --> 01:23:23,760
dark brown, sepia,

895
01:23:23,760 --> 01:23:25,920
khaki, clay,

896
01:23:25,920 --> 01:23:29,140
ochre, walnut, bronze,

897
01:23:29,140 --> 01:23:33,720
I was melting like a biscuit in milk.

898
01:23:33,720 --> 01:23:36,860
Every time the name of a color reached my ears,

899
01:23:36,860 --> 01:23:39,890
I felt the warmth on my cheeks,

900
01:23:39,890 --> 01:23:44,680
and I kept thinking about his caramel color eyes.

901
01:23:44,680 --> 01:23:45,650
raw sienna,

902
01:23:45,650 --> 01:23:48,450
I really don't want to let him go.

903
01:23:48,450 --> 01:23:49,960
Stay by my side.

904
01:23:49,960 --> 01:23:54,320
Always. So that I don't think about anything else,

905
01:23:54,320 --> 01:23:58,030
stay by my side and continue teaching me colors.

906
01:23:58,030 --> 01:23:59,970
valley mist, volcano,

907
01:23:59,970 --> 01:24:02,080
amber rust, foxy brown,

908
01:24:02,080 --> 01:24:07,940
If those eyes looked at me as if they were reproaching me, I wouldn't be able to bear it.

909
01:24:07,940 --> 01:24:12,860
Although I heard the names of many shades of brown, if those caramel color eyes

910
01:24:12,860 --> 01:24:17,720
start to resent me, I don't know what to call that color.

911
01:24:17,720 --> 01:24:19,190
whiskey, derby tan...

912
01:24:19,190 --> 01:24:24,450
The desolated Sahara desert. The cloudy London fog.

913
01:24:24,450 --> 01:24:30,920
The chili pepper that stimulates people. Should I call it all as the withering winter leaf?

914
01:24:30,920 --> 01:24:32,830
You seem lost in thought.

915
01:24:32,830 --> 01:24:33,980
What are you doing?

916
01:24:33,980 --> 01:24:37,620
Yeon Woo, there's something I want you to teach me.

917
01:24:37,620 --> 01:24:40,100
- What is it?
- Grayscale.

918
01:24:40,100 --> 01:24:43,970
The gray world you see.

919
01:24:49,840 --> 01:24:55,960
♫ Oh I will be fine. You don’t have to worry ♫

920
01:24:55,960 --> 01:25:01,520
♫ The way you look at me, I think about you again and again ♫

921
01:25:01,520 --> 01:25:07,610
♫ When our eyes meet, I am reborn ♫

922
01:25:07,610 --> 01:25:11,400
[Mom's World by Choi Yeon Woo class 1-3]

923
01:25:11,400 --> 01:25:17,310
Do you know how I felt when I discovered this?

924
01:25:17,310 --> 01:25:20,090
I felt sad.

925
01:25:20,090 --> 01:25:25,230
It felt endlessly sad.

926
01:25:25,230 --> 01:25:29,310
The color you see when I'm not with you.

927
01:25:29,310 --> 01:25:32,640
How does it look?

928
01:25:32,640 --> 01:25:35,380
I want to understand you.

929
01:25:35,380 --> 01:25:37,970
I want to know how you feel when you're alone.

930
01:25:37,970 --> 01:25:41,370
♫ This time, this love ♫

931
01:25:41,370 --> 01:25:45,310
Charcoal gray, mouse gray, snowy white, silver gray, silver,

932
01:25:45,310 --> 01:25:49,200
moon gray, cement gray, original gray.

933
01:25:51,780 --> 01:25:53,850
What does original gray mean?

934
01:25:53,850 --> 01:25:58,530
I just call it original gray because it can be confusing to just say gray.
(T/N: he's adding a descriptive word to a gray to differentiate them.)

935
01:25:58,530 --> 01:26:01,820
It's the original gray color everyone knows.

936
01:26:01,820 --> 01:26:03,760
Then, what about moon gray?

937
01:26:03,760 --> 01:26:07,100
Gray like the moon surface.

938
01:26:07,100 --> 01:26:11,180
It's good that there were some shades that I knew that you know.

939
01:26:11,180 --> 01:26:15,260
Snowy white, silver gray, cement gray and mouse gray are

940
01:26:15,260 --> 01:26:17,980
colors named after everyday objects.

941
01:26:17,980 --> 01:26:21,840
The colors of my world

942
01:26:21,840 --> 01:26:24,150
are also a part of Go Yoo Han's world.

943
01:26:24,150 --> 01:26:30,150
Yeon Woo, among these colors, which one is your favorite?

944
01:26:36,280 --> 01:26:38,330
Moon gray.

945
01:26:40,360 --> 01:26:44,820
It was the color of Mother's headband the day she disappeared.

946
01:26:44,820 --> 01:26:49,290
The color of the headband that my aunt doesn't remember.

947
01:26:58,230 --> 01:27:01,720
Decoloring? Even when I'm right next to him.

948
01:27:01,720 --> 01:27:03,780
I'm experiencing it?

949
01:27:06,950 --> 01:27:08,770
Yeon Woo.

950
01:27:15,760 --> 01:27:17,050
I'm okay.

951
01:27:17,050 --> 01:27:19,160
I'm going to leave first.

952
01:27:32,490 --> 01:27:35,360
What am I doing right now?

953
01:27:43,050 --> 01:27:46,160
A monster has appeared, Go Yoo Han.

954
01:27:46,160 --> 01:27:50,720
The female mantis eats the male mantis even during mating.

955
01:27:50,720 --> 01:27:56,200
The male mantis initiates mating even though it knows it will lose its life.

956
01:28:02,340 --> 01:28:05,880
[Breaking News: the head of the household in their forties, who's a Mono, murders their Probe spouse and their family, and commits suicide.]

957
01:28:26,460 --> 01:28:29,160
But you don't have to worry.

958
01:28:38,690 --> 01:28:42,610
I'll take the monster with me soon.

959
01:28:44,790 --> 01:28:49,540
The monster that wants to lock you up and obsess over you.

960
01:28:49,540 --> 01:28:53,430
But I'm different from other Monos.

961
01:28:53,430 --> 01:28:57,370
You showed me colors and let me experience joy.

962
01:28:57,370 --> 01:29:02,010
You, who gave me the experience of loss... Go Yoo Han.

963
01:29:02,010 --> 01:29:07,560
I will not make you miserable.

964
01:29:07,560 --> 01:29:09,720
Never.

965
01:29:12,120 --> 01:29:15,910
Goodbye, Go Yoo Han.

966
01:30:07,100 --> 01:30:09,000
Aunt...

967
01:30:10,500 --> 01:30:13,510
What's my name? What's your aunt's name?

968
01:30:13,510 --> 01:30:15,430
Yoo Yi Rang.

969
01:30:16,370 --> 01:30:17,880
Why are you asking me what your name is?

970
01:30:17,880 --> 01:30:20,380
To see if you're fully conscious.

971
01:30:20,380 --> 01:30:24,270
You've been in and out of consciousness for about ten days.

972
01:30:37,820 --> 01:30:42,800
Were you the one who saved me?

973
01:30:42,800 --> 01:30:48,280
Did you think I wouldn't know what you were up to? I know you.

974
01:30:52,590 --> 01:30:56,960
Your phone's been disconnected and I filled out your school transfer form.

975
01:30:56,960 --> 01:30:59,150
I also put our house on the market.

976
01:30:59,150 --> 01:31:02,800
Then, it's all over.

977
01:31:02,800 --> 01:31:06,430
Yes, it's all over.

978
01:31:06,430 --> 01:31:09,220
So, you just...

979
01:31:09,220 --> 01:31:11,830
you just have to pull yourself together.

980
01:31:14,480 --> 01:31:19,010
But... where are we?

981
01:31:19,010 --> 01:31:20,780
It doesn't look like a normal hospital.

982
01:31:20,780 --> 01:31:26,720
Well... it's a place that helps you and me both.

983
01:31:27,480 --> 01:31:33,200
No one knows we're here other than the two of us.

984
01:31:37,420 --> 01:31:42,670
My aunt clearly knows who I'm thinking of.

985
01:31:48,550 --> 01:31:51,380
[When needed]

986
01:31:54,830 --> 01:32:00,140
I'm trapped in this gray world once again.

987
01:32:00,140 --> 01:32:07,590
I need this much medicine every day to forget Go Yoo Han's number that is memorized in my head.

988
01:32:11,620 --> 01:32:15,860
My aunt is still searching for Mom's whereabouts.

989
01:32:15,860 --> 01:32:20,400
And I still miss Go Yoo Han.

990
01:32:24,360 --> 01:32:28,120
I must be seeing hallucinations as a result of all the medicine I took.

991
01:32:28,120 --> 01:32:32,590
It's a relief that I can at least see colors in my hallucination.

992
01:32:49,950 --> 01:32:51,790
Yoo Han!

993
01:32:54,750 --> 01:32:56,650
Hey!

994
01:33:00,560 --> 01:33:04,920
♫  Hug me so I’m not alone  ♫

995
01:33:04,920 --> 01:33:06,500
How are you here?

996
01:33:06,500 --> 01:33:09,390
Hey, did you think I wouldn't be able to find you?

997
01:33:09,390 --> 01:33:11,000
I'm your Probe.

998
01:33:11,000 --> 01:33:14,200
I can't. I shouldn't see you.

999
01:33:14,200 --> 01:33:17,320
Of course, you can, you idiot.

1000
01:33:17,320 --> 01:33:19,100
This is a dream, right?

1001
01:33:19,100 --> 01:33:21,390
I'm hallucinating because of all the pills, right?

1002
01:33:21,390 --> 01:33:22,840
I'm never waking up. Never.

1003
01:33:22,840 --> 01:33:25,390
Yeon Woo, look at me.

1004
01:33:25,390 --> 01:33:30,680
♫ Even if I’m far away, I'll always be there for you ♫

1005
01:33:30,680 --> 01:33:34,920
♫ When I think of you on a hard day ♫

1006
01:33:34,920 --> 01:33:39,010
♫ It’s a great consolation to me ♫

